PrecisEnactment of the NATIONAL PARKS OF CANADA LAND RENTS REMISSION ORDER, NO. 3 - which provides for the remission of some of the rent payable by those with a leasehold interest in public lands (a) situated within certain National Parks that are subject to a biennial or decennial rent-setting cycle, or (b) situated in the Town of Jasper, Alberta.
